# Component Conventions

## shadcn-vue (app/components/ui/)

- Install via `npx shadcn-vue@latest add <component>` — NEVER create manually
- Config: components.json (style: new-york, baseColor: stone, iconLibrary: lucide)
- Based on Reka UI headless primitives

## Domain Components (app/components/{domain}/)

- Group by feature domain: company/, price-list/, table/, form/, etc.
- Use TypeScript-first props with `defineProps<{}>()` + `withDefaults()`
- No `vue/require-default-prop` — use TypeScript defaults instead

## Form Pattern

```vue
<FormField v-slot="{ componentField }" name="fieldName">
  <FormItem>
    <FormLabel>Label</FormLabel>
    <FormControl>
      <Input v-bind="componentField" />
    </FormControl>
    <FormMessage />
  </FormItem>
</FormField>
```

## Icons

Use Lucide icons via `nuxt-lucide-icons` module (auto-imported).
